{"body": [{"indent": 0, "text": ["Basis"], "type": "title", "level": 0}, {"indent": 0, "type": "summary", "text": ["Provides operations for moving knots within the parametric space\nof a NURBS curve or surface."]}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "text": ["This op provides a set of operations applicable to the parametric space\nof spline curves and surfaces. The parametric space, also known as the\n\"domain\" of a NURBS or Bezier primitive, is defined by one basis in the\nU direction and, if the primitive is a surface, another basis in the V\ndirection. The size of the domain is given by the values of the knots\nthat make up the basis."]}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/images/BasisSOP.jpg", "scheme": "Image", "type": "link", "value": "../images/BasisSOP.jpg"}]}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "text": ["The Basis op contains both ratio-preserving and non ratio-preserving\noperations."]}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "text": ["If the basis reparameterization does not change the distance ratios\nbetween knots, the shape of a NURBS primitive is not affected. If the\nratios are not preserved; however, a NURBS primitive will change shape\nin the area influenced by the modified knots. Additionally, if the\nprimitive is a NURBS or Bezier surface, any profiles it may contain will\nbe affected as well."]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "text": ["Subset of spline primitives to operate on."]}], "indent": 4, "role": "item", "type": "parameters_item", "text": ["Group"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "text": ["Enables and disables transformations of the U basis below."]}], "indent": 4, "role": "item", "type": "parameters_item", "text": ["Edit the U Basis"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "text": ["Enables and disables transformations of the V basis below."]}], "indent": 4, "role": "item", "type": "parameters_item", "text": ["Edit the V Basis"]}], "container": true, "role": "item_group", "type": "parameters_item_group"}, {"body": [{"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "text": ["Parameterization method."]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 16, "type": "para", "text": ["Does not change the U basis."]}], "indent": 12, "type": "dt", "text": ["Unchanged"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 16, "type": "para", "text": ["Distributes all knots evenly."]}], "indent": 12, "type": "dt", "text": ["Uniform"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 16, "type": "para", "text": ["Computes knot ratios based on primitive chord length."]}], "indent": 12, "type": "dt", "text": ["Chord Length"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 16, "type": "para", "text": ["Similar to chord length, useful for sharp turns."]}], "indent": 12, "type": "dt", "text": ["Centripetal"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 16, "type": "para", "text": ["Edit knots of first spline primitive individually."]}], "indent": 12, "type": "dt", "text": ["Manual:Single"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 16, "type": "para", "text": ["Same as above but copy knots to all other primitives."]}], "indent": 12, "type": "dt", "text": ["Manual:Propagated"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 16, "type": "para", "text": ["Shift clusters of knots within the basis."]}], "indent": 12, "type": "dt", "text": ["Knotslide"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 16, "type": "para", "text": ["Computes knot ratio based on an approximate primitive arc length."]}], "indent": 12, "type": "dt", "text": ["Approximate Arc Length"]}], "container": true, "type": "dt_group"}], "indent": 8, "role": "item", "type": "parameters_item", "text": ["Parameterization"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "text": ["Editable field of knots in ascending order."]}], "indent": 8, "role": "item", "type": "parameters_item", "text": ["Knot Sequence"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "text": ["Reads knots of first primitive into the field above."]}], "indent": 8, "role": "item", "type": "parameters_item", "text": ["Read Basis"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "text": ["Area of the unit U domain to be shifted."]}], "indent": 8, "text": ["Range"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"channels": "/urange1 /urange2"}, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "text": ["Amount and direction of shift in knotslide."]}], "indent": 8, "text": ["Bias"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"channels": "/ubias"}, "type": "parameters_item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group", "type": "parameters_item_group"}], "indent": 4, "level": 2, "text": ["Parameterization"], "container": true, "type": "h", "id": null}, {"body": [{"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "text": ["Indicates whether bases should be concatenated."]}], "indent": 8, "role": "item", "type": "parameters_item", "text": ["Concatenate"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "text": ["New origin of the U basis."]}], "indent": 8, "text": ["Origin"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"channels": "/uorigin"}, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "text": ["New length of the U basis."]}], "indent": 8, "text": ["Length"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"channels": "/ulength"}, "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "text": ["Multiplier applied to basis at its origin."]}], "indent": 8, "text": ["Scale"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"channels": "/uscale"}, "type": "parameters_item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group", "type": "parameters_item_group"}], "indent": 4, "level": 2, "text": ["Map"], "container": true, "type": "h", "id": null}, {"body": [{"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "text": ["Enables and disables raising of the basis order."]}], "indent": 8, "role": "item", "type": "parameters_item", "text": ["Raise To"]}], "container": true, "role": "item_group", "type": "parameters_item_group"}], "indent": 4, "level": 2, "text": ["Order"], "container": true, "type": "h", "id": null}], "indent": 0, "level": 1, "text": "Parameters", "role": "section", "container": true, "type": "parameters_section", "id": "parameters"}, {"body": [], "usages": [{"body": [{"ref": "/examples/nodes/sop/polybridge/BridgeCurvesandPrims", "type": "include"}], "text": "BridgeCurvesandPrims", "type": "load_example", "attrs": {"path": "/examples/nodes/sop/polybridge/BridgeCurvesandPrims", "examplefile": "/examples/nodes/sop/polybridge/BridgeCurvesandPrims.otl", "examplefor": "/nodes/sop/polybridge"}}], "container": true, "level": 1, "text": "Examples", "role": "section", "type": "examples_section", "id": "examples"}], "summary": ["Provides operations for moving knots within the parametric space\nof a NURBS curve or surface."], "type": "root", "attrs": {"version": null, "tags": "curves, surfaces, splines, topology, cleanup", "namespace": null, "internal": "basis", "context": "sop", "type": "node", "icon": "SOP/basis"}, "title": ["Basis"]}